comment: Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with Morris (DET) that affects his RSBQ.
Jackson (DET) does not obtain a legal guarding position and makes body contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that affects his RSBQ.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Jackson's (DET) drive and spinning shot attempt.
Jackson (DET) and Middleton (MIL) briefly engage and separate.
L-SLA shows that Jackson (DET) makes incidental contact with Middleton (MIL) as he reaches for the ball.
Jackson (DET) makes contact with Middleton (MIL) that affects his RSBQ before the hook by Middleton.
Middleton (MIL) hooks Jackson (DET) as he drives to the rim.
Parker (MIL) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Drummond's (DET) shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the two rulings on the court that the ball did not make contact with the rim and that it was last touched by Monroe (MIL) before going OOB were upheld. The game clock was reset to 00:48.1 and shot clock to 8.
Jackson (DET) continues to move into Parker (MIL) on screen.
Monroe (MIL) makes contact with Harris's (DET) body that affects his driving shot attempt.

Jackson (DET) gathers between steps and lands on both feet. He lifts his right foot, which establishes his left as a pivot. Although he takes a high step with his right foot, he doesn't lift his left pivot before passing.
Jackson (DET) grabs and holds Middleton (MIL) affecting his FOM on the inbounds play.
Caldwell-Pope (DET) makes contact with Bayless (MIL) that affects his RSBQ.
Harris (DET) commits a take foul on Bayless (MIL).
Harris (DET) leaves his designated throw-in position.
Drummond (DET) delivers contact to Antetokounmpo (MIL) on the screen without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Morris (DET), Harris (DET), and Jackson (DET) all maintain legal guarding position as they contests Middleton's (MIL) half-court shot attempt.
